title: Did She Ever Find The Ring Her Brother Was Supposed To Propose With?
description:
Her brother was ready to propose to his girlfriend with their mother's engagement ring, but there's a problem! He gave the ring to his sister for safekeeping, but she lost it! Did she ever find the ring? We have an update!
